<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10611473>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Male genitalia of Dedalopterus lexuanhuei Pham, Ahrens and Sabatinelli, new species (holotype,A–C); D. malyszi Bunalski, 2001 (D–F). A, D, parameres in left lateral view; B, E, parameres in dorsal view. C, F, parameres in right lateral view. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10611473/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10611471>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Habitus in dorsal view. A–B, D. lexuanhuei Pham, Ahrens and Sabatinelli, new species. A, ♂ holotype; B, ♀ paratype; C–D, D. malyszi Bunalski, 2001 (Vietnam: Sa Pa; C, ♂; D, ♀). Scale bar: 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10611471/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

